          Welcome to edu-ai.asia. By using this website, you agree to comply with the following terms of service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Service Description</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          edu-ai.asia is a domain showcase and sales platform. We provide:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>Display of premium AI-related domains</li>
          <li>Domain information and use case introductions</li>
          <li>Domain purchase consultation services</li>
          <li>Domain transaction assistance</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          <strong>Important Notice:</strong> This website only provides information display and consultation services. Actual transactions are conducted through third-party escrow platforms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Domain Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Regarding domain information displayed on the website:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We strive to ensure information accuracy but do not guarantee absolute correctness</li>
          <li><strong>Availability:</strong> Domain availability may change at any time; actual availability is subject to verification</li>
          <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> Listed prices are for reference only; final prices are subject to negotiation</li>
          <li><strong>Updates:</strong> Information may be updated periodically without prior notice</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Transaction Process</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Domain transactions follow these principles:
        </p>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Inquiry Phase:</strong> Contact us via phone, email, or WeChat</li>
          <li><strong>Negotiation Phase:</strong> Discuss price, payment method, and delivery timeline</li>
          <li><strong>Escrow Transaction:</strong> Conduct secure transactions through third-party platforms (such as Escrow.com, Dan.com, etc.)</li>
          <li><strong>Domain Transfer:</strong> Assist with domain transfer after payment confirmation</li>
          <li><strong>Transaction Completion:</strong> Confirm successful domain transfer and close transaction</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          <strong>Security Guarantee:</strong> We strongly recommend using third-party escrow services to protect the rights of both buyers and sellers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
