          By using this website, you agree to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>Provide truthful and accurate contact information</li>
          <li>Not engage in fraudulent or illegal activities</li>
          <li>Respect intellectual property and trademark rights</li>
          <li>Comply with relevant laws and regulations</li>
          <li>Assume legal responsibility for domain usage</li>
        </ul>
