          <li>We make no guarantees regarding the commercial value, investment returns, or future performance of domains</li>
          <li>We are not responsible for potential trademark or copyright issues related to domains</li>
          <li>We are not responsible for the service quality of third-party platforms</li>
          <li>We are not liable for any indirect losses arising from the use of this website</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          <strong>Recommendation:</strong> Before purchasing a domain, please conduct your own trademark searches and legal consultations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
