          The design, content, trademarks, and other intellectual property of this website belong to edu-ai.asia. Without permission, they may not be copied, modified, distributed, or used for commercial purposes. Displayed domains belong to their respective owners.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          In case of disputes:
        </p>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <li>First attempt to resolve through friendly negotiation</li>
          <li>If negotiation fails, seek third-party mediation</li>
